data.label: API usage over time
data.query:
SELECT CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp) year_Timestamp, ApiFamily, 
CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp) month_Timestamp, DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp) day_Timestamp,
 HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) hour_Timestamp, COUNT(Id) 
 FROM ApiTotalUsageEventLog 
 GROUP BY CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp), ApiFamily, CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp), 
 DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp), HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) ORDER BY CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp) ASC, 
 ApiFamily ASC, CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp) ASC, DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp) ASC, 
 HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) ASC LIMIT 250

data.label: Failed API Calls
data.query: SELECT CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp) year_Timestamp, ApiFamily, CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp) month_Timestamp, DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp) day_Timestamp, HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) hour_Timestamp, COUNT(Id) FROM ApiTotalUsageEventLog WHERE StatusCode >= 400 AND StatusCode <= 500 GROUP BY CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp), ApiFamily, CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp), DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp), HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) ORDER BY CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp) DESC LIMIT 250

data.label: Apex Errors per hour
data.query: SELECT CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp) year_Timestamp, CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp) month_Timestamp, DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp) day_Timestamp, HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) hour_Timestamp, COUNT(Id) FROM ApexUnexpectedExcpEventLog GROUP BY CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp), CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp), DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp), HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) ORDER BY CALENDAR_YEAR(Timestamp) ASC, CALENDAR_MONTH(Timestamp) ASC, DAY_IN_MONTH(Timestamp) ASC, HOUR_IN_DAY(Timestamp) ASC LIMIT 250
